===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To [[petition]] or [[solicit]] help from a [[supernatural]] or higher being.
# To humbly [[beg]] a person for [[aid]] or their [[time]].
# {{cattag|Christianity}} to [[talk]] to [[God]] for any reason.

